(v)          
No Government Obligor.   None of the Receivables is due
from the United States of America or any state or from any agency,
department or instrumentality of the United States of America or
any state.
 

(vi)         
Security Interest in Financed Equipment.   Immediately
prior to the sale, assignment and transfer thereof, each Receivable
